{"tid":643962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾被生蝦刺傷 男士染食肉菌亡","createTime":"2018-04-27T01:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T01:54:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"da6449319c6259945ed73c66678441aca99c5a1a","tid":643962,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T01:44:13.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】本港新增一宗俗稱食肉菌感染的壞死性筋膜炎個案。根據衞生防護中心最新一期《傳染病直擊》，一名41歲有長期病患港男上周一（16日）出現發燒、肌肉痛、腹瀉及右下肢疼痛腫脹等症狀，3日後往伊利沙伯醫院求醫，院方發現其左腳下肢青腫及皮膚出現斑點，臨床診斷為雙腳出現壞死性筋膜炎，進行雙腿截肢，其後一直於深切治療部留醫，其右腳組織及傷口樣本經化驗後，發現帶創傷弧菌，患者最終在22日因併發敗血性休克及多重器官衰竭死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據家屬指，患者每日均到街市，近日無外遊記錄，發病當日曾於家中處理從樂富街市購得的生蝦，期間有刺傷手指，認為是其中一個風險因素，中心已將個案轉交死因庭跟進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/90e..gxZw7sBBz44qzKhhA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/27JAC002__20180427_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F90e..gxZw7sBBz44qzKhhA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F27JAC002__20180427_L.jpg&h=ff3a0694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%9D%A6%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B7-%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E6%9F%93%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%89%E8%8F%8C%E4%BA%A1-224548803.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%259D%25A6%25E5%2588%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259F%2593%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2589%25E8%258F%258C%25E4%25BA%25A1-224548803.html&d=VtJmn0fRqBpAsJTqRyfaYDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0d34c4b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9B%BE%E8%A2%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%9D%A6%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B7-%E7%94%B7%E5%A3%AB%E6%9F%93%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%89%E8%8F%8C%E4%BA%A1-224548803.html</a>"},{"pid":"3028b9081f05a241f21662c8cac27628885ac1a2","tid":643962,"uid":98163,"like":564,"dislike":0,"score":564,